Zonal Wind (U) Descriptive Time Series analysis by location

Shu Wei

Reading data

load("D:/UCR/CIMPA/Gauss server/Emuladores/datos/U_Global.Rdata")
y1 <- U_Global %>% filter(lat>=30 & lat<=31 & lon>=240 & lon <=241)
y2 <- U_Global %>% filter(lat>=30 & lat<=31 & lon>=260 & lon <=261)
y3 <- U_Global %>% filter(lat>=30 & lat<=31 & lon>=291 & lon <=292)
y4 <- U_Global %>% filter(lat>=41 & lat<=42 & lon>=240 & lon <=241)
y5 <- U_Global %>% filter(lat>=41 & lat<=42 & lon>=260 & lon <=261)
y6 <- U_Global %>% filter(lat>=41 & lat<=42 & lon>=291 & lon <=292)
y7 <- U_Global %>% filter(lat>=51 & lat<=52 & lon>=240 & lon <=241)
y8 <- U_Global %>% filter(lat>=51 & lat<=52 & lon>=260 & lon <=261)
y9 <- U_Global %>% filter(lat>=51 & lat<=52 & lon>=291 & lon <=292)

datos <- data.frame(y1[,1:2],y1$U,y2$U,y3$U,y4$U,y5$U,y6$U,y7$U,y8$U,y9$U)
colnames(datos)[3:11]<-c("y1","y2","y3","y4","y5","y6","y7","y8","y9")
names(datos)
##  [1] "Year"  "Month" "y1"    "y2"    "y3"    "y4"    "y5"    "y6"    "y7"   
## [10] "y8"    "y9"
datos.ts<-ts(datos[,-c(1,2)])
autoplot(datos.ts)

autoplot(datos.ts, facets = TRUE)

Spectral analysis

# Spectral Analysis
par(mfrow=c(1,2))
raw.spec1 <- spec.pgram(y1, taper = 0)
plot(raw.spec1, log = "no")

raw.spec4 <- spec.pgram(y4, taper = 0)
plot(raw.spec4, log = "no")

ts.plot(datos.ts, col=1:9)
spec = mvspec(datos.ts, spans=c(3,3), taper=.1)

Wavelets analysis
